            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Dictate Anywhere 2.2.7

- Adjusted AI transcript cleanup prompts to use the original, more faithful wording for paragraph and list structuring.
- Reduced overly aggressive transcript restructuring so cleaned text stays closer to what the speaker actually said.
- Kept the em dash cleanup safeguard in place so processed transcripts continue avoiding em dashes.
]]></description>
